jqlQueryForNewTickets: project = PPS and status = New ORDER BY createdDate DESC
jqlQueryForMSR: project = PPS AND labels in (EDT, RES) AND created >= 2019-10-01 AND created <= 2019-11-01
jqlQueryForAgedTkts: project = PPS AND status in (New, Reopened, "In QA", "Test Review", "In Progress", "Ready for Analysis", "On Hold", "3rd Party - Pending")
